# obrr

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of obrr is to fetch time series of the latest OBR projections.

## Installation

You can install the development version of obrr from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("l-hodge/obrr")
```
